    dc:title "A new genus and a new species of Schizomyiina (Diptera: Cecidomyiidae: Asphondyliini) inducing petiole galls on Macaranga bancana (Miq.) in Borneo, Malaysia" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1440474>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1440476>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1440478>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1440480> ;
